title: On The Photodisintegration of V-51, Ni, Mn-55, and Co-59.

x4freetext: ON THE PHOTODISINTEGRATION OF V-51, NI, MN-55,
TORINO   AND  INSTITUTO NAZIONALE DI FISICA NUCLEARE,

x4codes.shortRef: Jour: Nuclear Physics, Section A, Vol.122, Issue.1, p.49 (1968)

x4codes.hlp: Universita degli Studi di Torino + INFN Torino, Italy

x4freetext: . A DIFFUSION CLOUD CHAMBER FILLED WITH HELIUM AT
PARALLEL TO THE DIRECTION OF THE GAMMA-RAY BEAM.
THE USUAL INTERPRETATION OF THE PHOTONEUTRON SPECTRA
IN TERMS OF EVAPORATION WITH A SMALL CONTRIBUTION
OF DIRECT REACTION IS NOT IN AGREEMENT WITH
THE EXPERIMENTAL RESULTS FOR NEUTRON ENERGIES LOWER
THAN 1.5 MEV. QUALITATIVE DISCUSSION OF OTHER MODELS
IS GIVEN TO EXPLAIN THE EXPERIMENTAL INDICATION OF
PHOTONEUTRON POLARIZATION FOUND FOR MN-55 AND CO-59.
DETAILED DESCRIPTION OF THE EXPERIMENT IS IN THE PAPER
.DATA WERE COMPILED IN SCJAD OF SARATOV STATE
